//      TEXT    others              OK
//  [Firefox+XMLHttpRequest]
//      XML     text/xml            OK
//      XML     application/rdf+xml OK (overrideMimeType)
//      TEXT    text/plain          OK
//      TEXT    others              OK (overrideMimeType)
